  "method": [
    "Take the honey, milk, butter, lime zest, bay leaf, and lime juice to a",
    "boil in a medium skillet.",
    "In a medium mixing cup, whisk together the eggs, vegetable oil, and",
    "salt with a rolling pin.",
    "Stir in the flour until you have a stiff, bushy dough.",
    "Create 4-inch squares out of the string. Repeat with the rest of the",
    "dough.",
    "Warm 2 inches of peanut oil to 360° in a big saucepan.",
    "Bake 3 minutes over medium fire, rotating once, until golden brown.",
    "Heat the sugar syrup again.",
    "Transfer a few baked goods at a time to the honey syrup and switch to",
    "cover with tongs.",
    "Move to a big mixing bowl and toss with chopped nuts and spices.",
    "Repeat the process till all the pastries have been coated."
